grammar_point: ～は～の一つだ
jlpt: N4
meaning: 〜 is one of (many) 〜
meaning_warning: null
details:
  Register: Standard
  使用域: 一般
writeup: In order to express that something is only one thing from within a larger category, the construction～は～の一つだwill
  be used. In this expression, (A), the thing that there is one of, will be followed byは. After this,
  (B) +の一つだwill highlight the broader category to which (A) belongs.In this grammar point,の一つis a standard
  counter. This means that other counters can and will be used, when they are more appropriate than一つ.
examples:
  - japanese: アンドロイドはスマートフォンのOSの一つだ。
    english: Android is one of (many) smartphone operating systems.
  - japanese: 電車は乗り物の一つです。
    english: Trains are one of (many) vehicles.
  - japanese: 彼も家族の一人だ。
    english: He is also one member of my family.
  - japanese: トマトはフルーツの一種だ。
    english: Tomatoes are one of many types of fruits.
  - japanese: このクレヨンはこのセットの一本だ。
    english: This crayon is part of this set.
  - japanese: ホンダは車のメーカーの一つだ。
    english: Honda is one of (many) car makers.
  - japanese: アイフォンはスマートフォンの一つだ。
    english: iPhone is one of (many) smartphones.
  - japanese: 文法は大事な勉強の一つです。
    english: Grammar is one of (many) important things to study.
  - japanese: コカコーラはコーラの一つだ。
    english: Coca-cola is one of many colas.
  - japanese: 寿司は日本の有名な食べ物の一つだ。
    english: Sushi is one of many famous Japanese foods.
url: https://bunpro.jp/grammar_points/は-の一つだ
false_friends:
  - term: ～のうち(で)
    meaning: Of the, Among(st)
    kind: synonym
